title: Woody Herman - 1985 Interview on the S/S Norway
description: Woody Herman is interviewed for closed curcuit TV on the S/S Norway Cruise Ship in 1985.  Rare video seen only onboard the ship features Woody, Major Holly, Gary Burton and Buddy Tate.
